      • compare

        public static <V> int compare(V v1,
              V v2)
        compare two object
          About result
        • if v1 > v2, return 1
        • if v1 = v2, return 0
        • if v1 < v2, return -1
          About rule
        • if v1 is null, v2 is null, then return 0
        • if v1 is null, v2 is not null, then return -1
        • if v1 is not null, v2 is null, then return 1
        • return v1.Comparable.compareTo(Object)
        参数:
        v1 -
        v2 -
        返回:
